node.title: Two people seriously injured in Waitakaruru crash - reports
node.description: The serious crash unit has been notified.
node.content: ["There are reports of serious injuries in a two-vehicle crash on State Highway 2 near Waitakaruru in the Waikato.", "Emergency services were called to the collision at 2:15pm on Wednesday. Police say the indications are two people have been seriously injured in the crash.", "\"SH2 is closed between Okaeria Road and the SH25 roundabout and diversions are in place,\" a police spokesperson says.", "\"Police advise motorists to expect delays and avoid the area if at all possible.\"", "The serious crash unit has been notified."]
